{"tid":749884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵👱🏻‍♂️：已準備好對5000億美元中國進口品課徵關稅","createTime":"2018-07-20T11:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T08:41:10.000Z","uid":13663,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cb24d1476713713e54e57af2f03d6125792588eb","tid":749884,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T11:45:48.000Z","msg":"川普：已準備好對5000億美元中國進口品課徵關稅<br />\n用LINE傳送 +<br />\n留言<br />\n2018-07-20 18:59經濟日報 記者易起宇╱即時報導<br />\n美國總統川普表示，若有需要，他有意對所有進口到美國的中國產品課徵關稅。此消息一出，美股期指跌勢立刻擴大。<br />\n<br />\n川普接受CNBC專訪時表示：「我準備好將數字拉高到5,000億美元。」據美國人口普查局數據，這個數字約莫就是中國2017年進口到美國的產品金額（精確數字為5,055億美元），而當年美國出口到中國的產品金額只有1,299億美元。"},{"pid":"bc10d704cb8243a2bf7c1160175935a976183fae","tid":749884,"uid":73915,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T11:47:38.000Z","msg":"好撚仆街<br />\n次次亞洲收市先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93642286cef6368a7508a6dd148e0d2d8c195af2","tid":749884,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T17:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324349f9737c7998d403e4df6e3a0634a92311e6","tid":749884,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T08:40:21.000Z","msg":"由10%上到25%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4731573b247e83c0d7dc74de12b1715e567da7a5","tid":749884,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T08:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83d80a10de67ee2cb419bfa323421a045163b0f","tid":749884,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T08:41:10.000Z","msg":"有得震無得訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}